{
  "stem": "24364.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And eventually, in-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] in the beginning of-- I think in February of 1945, we got amnesty.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so there were preparation for us to leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But again, something interfered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "First of all, it was difficult to get shipping at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And second, there was a big polio epidemic in Mauritius and we were quarantined for a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were lots of people who died at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was really one of the largest epidemics, I heard, in the whole world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there were quite a few people, even from the US, came to Mauritius at that time to check-- I mean physicians or scientists-- to check out that epidemic.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we had five cases in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "One of them died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we were quarantined for a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then there were a couple of-- three, as a matter of fact-- cyclones on Mauritius, which we had never experienced during the-- it's strange-- during the five years.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "All of a sudden, there were three in a row.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that was-- they really devastated the island.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so again, we were delayed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we made it only after the war ended.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We left Mauritius on August, I believe the 12th, 1945, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on the which was a British troop ship.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And again, it took about-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] took a little less, I think.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made it in two weeks this time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we arrived in-- in Palestine on the 26th of August, 1945.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was our odyssey.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What was it like, arriving in-- in Palestine?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
